# F6 real Google Calendar executor (see docs/f6-google-calendar-runbook.md).
# Set EXECUTION_MODE to google_calendar (or local,google_calendar), the target
# calendar id, and mount the service-account key via docker-compose.override.yml.
# COMPANION_V2_EXECUTION_MODE=google_calendar
# COMPANION_V2_GOOGLE_CALENDAR_ID=your-calendar-id@group.calendar.google.com
# GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS=/secrets/gcal-sa.json

